snippet.title: Mamma Mia - Mamma Mia | 맘마미아 - Episode 7:  'Sons Over Flowers' Special! (2013.06.16)
snippet.description:
Stars and their mothers share special stories. Seo Inguk, Nichkhun, Kevin, Niel and Choi Byeongcheol. It's a special with all the charming men. The sons show off their charms. The 'Sons Over Flowers' special.
